description: This header file declares APIs for managing GRE object parameters, including functions to get and set string parameters related to GRE configuration within the COSA Data Model Library.

methods.name: Gre_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves the value of a string parameter for the GRE object, given the parameter name.

methods.name: Gre_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets the value of a string parameter for the GRE object, given the parameter name and new value.
